  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting the Rohingya Cultural Memory Centre</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to provide Rohingya refugees in the camps in Cox&#x2019;s Bazar with a creative and safe space where they can share their knowledge, preserve their cultural heritage, and reconnect with their individual and collective memory. Through this effort, IOM is working towards addressing the loss of identity endured by the Rohingya refugee population, counteracting the cultural limitations they have faced, and, more so now, the monotony and isolation that has resulted from their displacement.</narrative>
  </description>
